Class Object2D

  • java.lang.Object
    • Object2D
  • public class Object2D
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents object in 2D space with properties for kinematics (modelled as a point particle but with orientation).

      • orientation

        public double orientation
        Stores the orientation of object. This is defined as the angle between the positive x-axis and the object's line of sight.
